sg":"林睿睎稱，包括學生事務處在內的中大高層曾接觸內閣，暗示他們要在上任前辭職，<strong>「否則會搞埋學生會代表會及其他中央學生組織」</strong>。他說，內閣不少成員及其親友收死亡恐嚇，令內閣不得不撤回參選文件，此舉令「朔夜」的民意授權失效，故需就此負政治責任，全體辭職。他強調，撤回參選文件並非與校方有「枱底交易」，以換取校方撤銷針對學生會的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210301/s00001/1614590585154/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210301%2Fs00001%2F1614590585154%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt177WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=87e9b410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210301%2Fs00001%2F1614590585154%2F&h=f4fac885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210301/s00001/1614590585154/</a>"},{"pid":"6c8a5e1a6de511a65cf826296f3a3235b71e165f","tid":2428553,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7574f85b4bcbca1efc965d23bae6c2022a33516d","tid":2428553,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"一定係用濃濃嘅愛共情操嚟感化學生會啦"},{"pid":"80d7a0a60361f149b04c32ffcf1945aac8eb1496","tid":2428553,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7574f85b4bcbca1efc965d23bae6c2022a33516d","tid":2428553,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"一定係用濃濃嘅愛共情操嚟感化學生會啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"不幸中萬幸 學生會成員冇被退學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLuKMIYBDJP/\" data-sr-